DOGS WERE OKAY SO WE SLEPT IN THE CAR UNTIL THE SNOWPLOW CAME IN THE MORNING. I DECLARE UNDER PENALTY OF PERJURY UNDER THE LAWS OF THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA THAT THE FOREGOING IS TRUE AND CORRECT."
